#. Tag: title
#: fundamentals.docbook:2
#, no-c-format
msgid "Some Fundamentals"
msgstr "Nekaj osnov"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:4
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kwrite; and many other &katepart; users are very simple to use. Anyone that "
"has used a text editor should have no problems."
msgstr ""
"&kwrite; in mnogi drugi &katepart; Uporabniki so zelo enostavni za uporabo. "
"Kdor je uporabljal urejevalnik besedil, ne bi smel imeti težav."

#. Tag: title
#: fundamentals.docbook:10
#, no-c-format
msgid "Drag and Drop"
msgstr "Povleci in spusti"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:12
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&katepart; uses the &kde; Drag and Drop protocol. Files may be dragged and "
"dropped onto &katepart; from the Desktop, the filemanager &dolphin;, or some "
"remote &FTP; site opened in one of &dolphin;'s windows."
msgstr ""
"&katepart; uporablja &kde; Protokol povleci in spusti. Datoteke lahko "
"povlečete in spustite na &katepart; z namizja, upravitelja datotek &dolphin; "
"ali kakšnega oddaljenega &FTP; spletno mesto, odprto v enem od oken "
"&dolphin;."

#. Tag: title
#: fundamentals.docbook:20
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shortcuts"
msgstr "Bližnjice"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:22
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Many of the shortcuts are configurable by way of the <link linkend="
"\"settings-help-menu\">Settings</link> menu. By default &katepart; honors "
"the following shortcuts:"
msgstr ""
"Številne bližnjice je mogoče konfigurirati v meniju <link linkend=\"settings-"
"help-menu\">Nastavitve</link>. Privzeto &katepart; spoštuje naslednje "
"bližnjice:"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:29
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ins;"
msgstr "&Ins;"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:30
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Toggle between Insert and Overwrite mode. When in insert mode the editor "
"will add any typed characters to the text while pushing along any data to "
"the right of the text cursor. Overwrite mode causes the entry of each "
"character to eliminate the character immediately to the right of the text "
"cursor."
msgstr ""
"Preklapljaj med načinoma Vrini in Prepiši. Ko je v načinu vrivanja, bo "
"urejevalnik besedilu dodal katerikoli vtipkan znak, medtem ko bo katerekoli "
"podatke desno od kurzorja pomaknil naprej. Način prepisovanja povzroči, da "
"bo vsak vnos uničil znak desno od kurzorja."

